[330.425998, "o", "He didn't say any more, but we've always been unusually communicative in a reserved way, and I understood that he meant a great deal more than that. In consequence, I'm inclined to reserve all judgments, a custom that has opened up many odd natures to me and also made me the prey of not a few veteran bores. The abnormal mind is quick to detect and attach itself to this trait when it appears in a normal person, and so it came about that in college I was unjustly accused of being a politician, bec"]
[330.426582, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@b419d4b4dbd9:/app# "]
